'''CT-5'''<ref name="Guide">{{InsiderCite|84|Guide to the Grand Army of the Republic}}</ref>, also referred to as the '''CT 5-series''',<ref name="DB">{{DB|organization|clonetrooperpilots|clone trooper pilots}}</ref> was a famous batch<ref name="Guide" /> of [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone trooper]] [[Clone trooper pilot/Legends|pilots]] that were recognized as the best trained to pilot [[Jadthu-class landing ship/Legends|''Jadthu''-class landing ships]].<ref name="DB" /> [[Clone Commander/Legends|Clone Commander]] [[Jai'galaar (clone)|Jai'galaar]] was a member of this batch who commanded the [[127th Gunship Wing]] and was later demoted to [[Clone Captain/Legends|captain]] after the [[Retreat at Katraasii]].<ref name="Guide" />

